    "The collaborative coding process, as outlined, involves six progressive steps: (1) preliminary scrutiny and planning, (2) open and axial coding, (3) development of a preliminary codebook, (4) pilot testing of the codebook, (5) final coding procedures, and (6) reviewing the codebook and deriving themes.",
    "This study followed these steps in the labeling process.",
    "Using a random sampling algorithm, 1000 records were chosen from the complete dataset for coding analysis.",
    "During the initial stage of the coding analysis, the dataset was thoroughly examined, compared, conceptualized, and categorized.",
    "The coding scheme for classifying misinformation, fake news, and propaganda on online platforms was adapted from previous studies that categorized fake news and rumors."
  ],
